G A M E N O T E S

You led the revolution that freed the People's Republic
of Basenji from the shackles of a corrupt monarchy. But
now the new regime will be tested. You are the Glorious
Leader who must hold onto power by maintaining the
delicate balance between the interests of
fundamentalists, capitalists, patriots, and liberals
However be aware, your brother, Farouk, consolidates
power and influence with the intention to overthrow you!
How will you manage affairs with your neighboring
countries while ensuring you don't attract too much
negative attention from the Americans? Will you be a
generous donor to the United Nations? Or an
international pariah building nuclear weapons in secret?
The choice is yours in Rogue State
